  <summary date="2023-12-07T16:06:22Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Stop Arctic Ocean Drilling Act of 2023

This bill prohibits the Department of the Interior from issuing or extending a lease or any other authorization for the exploration, development, or production of oil, natural gas, or any other mineral in the Arctic areas of the Outer Continental Shelf.</summary>
